issue.title: Food name dictionary for better words search
issue.body:
Implement a dictionary of food names to help match with the content, that way we'll have lots more words to search for youtube videos. It's important to measure how many times and the importance of the word in the word into the pages context.

For this, I think will be better use some backend.

issue.title: Detect nationality and adds better tag complement
issue.body: So far, every word or category found on DOM is added by the word 'recipe' for the search, so it searchs by 'burguer recipe' ou 'sandwiches recipe'. But, when word is a nationality, would be better search for 'brazilian food' instead of 'brazilian recipe'.
